# Object Property: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox> (personal mailbox)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox> "A  personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox> "personal mailbox")
